Write your message here. This is the message that gets sent to every new connection after you accept their invite.

Keep it:
- Warm and personal (not a sales pitch)
- Under ~500 characters
- Ending with a clear call-to-action (e.g. a calendar link, a question, a resource)

Example:
---
Hi! Thanks for connecting. I'm [YOUR NAME] — [one line about what you do or care about].

Would love to connect properly — feel free to book time here: [YOUR CALENDAR LINK]
